- Unvarnished, detail‑forward mixes that preserve midrange nuance: The “raw, confessional” and “detail‑forward” character promises preservation of midrange warmth and vocal nuance (no glossy reverb burying the voice), fitting my value for midrange detail and emotionally direct vocals.
