- Aesthetic fit overall: My retained mid‑90s alt tastes (confessional, raw vocal immediacy, restrained mastering) are literally what Candidate 2 promises. Candidate 1, while technically well‑made and partially aligned (tube warmth, preserved dynamics), leans toward a glossy, spacious pop‑soul presentation that conflicts with my dislike of over‑spacious/glossy production and radio sheen.
